	The goal of the College of Engineering - Boise is to offer outstanding graduate engineering instruction, research, continuing education, and outreach services for individuals and businesses in Idaho and throughout the Northwest.  The focus of educational activities is on innovative master's and doctoral programs uniquely suited for the engineer in industry or full-time students.  Externally funded research is solicited from both government and industry sources, with an emphasis on application of advanced design and manufacturing processes.  Thesis topics and projects for degree requirements can be tied to ongoing industry activity.  Short courses in specialized areas are provided to help practicing engineers gain additional skills to stay professionally current.
	<p>
	In addition to services we provide in Boise, we can facilitate your access to the College of Engineering in Moscow.  Our college is the premier engineering program in the State of Idaho and among the best in the Northwest.  Whether you seek a graduate degree in engineering, or advanced skills for a solution to your technical problems, the University of Idaho is eager to help.</font></td>
